pwd---present work directory
cd---change directory
ls---list of file
mkdir--to make new folder
touch----create new file
vi----its a editor
cd ..----one step back
cd----root directory
cd ~/----directly jump to a specific folder from anywhere
cat----to view what file contains

how to use and close vi editor---first press 'i' then write your content then press 'ESC' then Shift+: then type wq then enter

grep----to get string value from a file 
